title: DDFP 470: Rashad Jennings, 2016 Jets & 'Bachelorette' recap
itunes:title: DDFP 470: Rashad Jennings, 2016 Jets & 'Bachelorette' recap
description:
Shek is first joined by Dan Hanzus and Giants running back Rashad Jennings to discuss the top current RBs in the NFL, the best all-star games and Rashad's expectations for the Giants in 2016. Shek and Dan are then joined by Marc Istook and Lindsay Rhodes to review the Jets' 2016 schedule and participate in another edition of "Surprise Game Show." Finally, the show wraps with an in-depth recap of the latest episode of "The Bachelorette."
